elided out [...]. The problem you see

 >>> gcc -m64 -std=gnu99 -shared -O2 -g -pipe -Wall -Wp,-D_FORTIFY_SOURCE=2 
-fexceptions -fstack-protector-strong --param=ssp-buffer-size=4 
